channel.title: Computer not letting me open IPconfig..?
channel.description:
Well, i was recently port forwarding... and it says to click Run > Search > Ipconfig
I click it, and it opens and closes really quick...
If it helps i have Windows 7. What do i do???
Could i just use 1 of Googles systems to check my Computers IP? :D?

item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

If that doesnt work once in cmd type
C:/Windows/system32/ipconfig
